Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.16,0:22:45.42,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}sakamichi wo sora he noboreba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:51.93,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}wakareyuku suisei no mizuumi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:57.27,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}mikansei na bokutachi dakara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.27,0:23:04.35,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}kizutsukezu ni irarenai
