Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:29.67,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}ai suru hito ha kitto soba ni iru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:36.04,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}taisetsu na mono wa itsumo soba ni aru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:19.13,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}The two of us who fell for each other
