Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:37.36,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}to the perfect world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.16,0:22:45.42,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}If you climb the hill towards the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:51.93,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}there flows the comet river
