Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.19,0:23:16.45,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}I feel like we'll touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:23.12,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}If you can embrace me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:29.67,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}Your beloved will surely be by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:36.04,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}Those important to you will always be by your side
